JAVASCRIPT
----------
- Click on a sea creature image (whale, turtle, jellyfish) to mark it as found; 
  - Page dynamically updates the "found" count below each creature and 
  - Shows a congratulatory message when all of that creature type are found. 
- Includes a Light/Dark Mode toggle button that changes background images dynamically based on 
  - screen size (desktop/mobile)
  - light/dark mode.

